title: EP.52: SEATTLES HUGE WIN, PACKERS STRUGGLES, STEELERS DEFENSE, MAJOR PERFORMANCES AND MUCH MORE!
description: Week one is here and football is finally back in our lives. After that Monday night game I'm sure we are all shocked especially with the Broncos weird decision not to call a timeout and their weirder decision to kick a 64 yard field goal. Anyways we cover A LOT of football in this episode and Griffin explains why the Packers beatdown is encouraging. Joe goes over why the Steelers win is a big loss and trust me we get into a lot of other topics. TUNE IN!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
